did.unittitle: Stanford University, International Relations Program, honors theses
did.abstract: Honors theses written by undergraduate students in the Stanford University International Relations Program.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents note
scopecontent.p: The collection consists of honors theses written by undergraduate students in the Stanford University International Relations Program.

acqinfo.head: Acquisition Information
acqinfo.p: Theses were transferred to the Stanford University Archives from the International Relations Program in several accessions between 2004 and 2010. Additional theses were received from the Hume Writing Center in 2011.

accessrestrict.head: Access to Collection
accessrestrict.p: The collection is open for research; materials must be requested at least 48 hours in advance of intended use. No photocopies may be made.

userestrict.head: Publication Rights
userestrict.p: Copyright is retained by the creators for materials they have authored or otherwise produced. Transmission or reproduction of materials requires the written permission of the copyright owner.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation note
prefercite.p: [Identification of item], Stanford University, International Relations Program, Honors Theses (6526). Dept. of Special Collections and University Archives, Stanford University Libraries, Stanford, Calif.
